{"tid":1762702,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理寄： 一人一張聖誕咭，寄比美國議員","createTime":"2019-11-29T18:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T01:10:45.000Z","uid":263648,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9c3f3e2822fb490960a7c937fe43f742fe4e65","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和你寄聖誕咭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n按照你生日月份，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一人寄九張咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>比美國議員Co-sponsors、Trump及Sharon姨姨，感謝佢地推動香港人權與民主法。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收實體聖誕咭會好開心。收到成堆咭，可吸引外媒報導。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都係另類文宣。我地唔淨係得負面新聞，比D大愛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收咭名單如下，要盡快在12月頭寄出</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=66032ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb/view?usp=sharing</a> (EXCEL)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=3dab49e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u/view?usp=sharing</a>(PDF)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[b]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">綜合各方意見的重點收咭人士(有時間就每個都寄)</span></span></span></strong>:</ins></strong><br />\nMarco Rubio  (Sen.)<br />\nNancy Pelosi (Speaker)<br />\nChristopher H. Smith (Rep.)<br />\nRick Scott  (Sen.)<br />\nJosh Hawley (Sen.)<br />\nTed Cruz (Sen.)<br />\nJames E. Risch (Sen.)<br />\nMitch McConnell (Sen.)<br />\nJames P. McGovern (Rep.)<br />\nAngus S. King Jr. (Sen.)<br />\nDonald Trump (President)<br />\nSharon Hom (Adjunct Professor, New York University)<br />\nSolomon Yue (Committeeman)<br />\n<br />\n有錯漏請更正。<br />\n<br />\n重要事項: 香港郵局已於2019年11月26日截空郵，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但仍可寄出聖誕咭</span></strong>，美國需要7至16個工作天處理，聖誕咭可能遲於聖誕節收到。因此請同時祝福Happy New Year。另外<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家提及Hong Kong Be Water Act</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n郵費: HK$4.9一張咭，重量限制為 20g, 尺吋不大於16.5cm x 24.5cm; 厚度限制為5mm;  如擔心重量超過20g但少於30g，請貼上HK$7.4的郵票。<br />\n<br />\n抱歉暫時未能安排代收郵件。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好幫襯&quot;三中商&quot;之類的書局。"},{"pid":"8311b79906e9bd7b0afdf639d5199579211b09ee","tid":1762702,"uid":30604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"和理非 assemble"},{"pid":"a6c648dbbfd748d85ad20b172aaa6288724e1434","tid":1762702,"uid":313498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"ff598afbaa0a70b725ff687d87807a4e8283bd08","tid":1762702,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:07:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a819c8dac0e411ceff8e5df069a5fd9f98f91ce6","tid":1762702,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:07:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf41c8a030e66c0f3c88d4b6e170f303