02:41:10.000Z","msg":"如果需要聖誕卡我有若干數量可以提供，大概20-30張，有需要可以搵我，免費郵寄畀你寫：）<br />\n可以選擇有信封定無信封，本身係postcard 黎嘅。"},{"pid":"cd186ada41b027704356149b602525760f1b4ef7","tid":1762702,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7392a6812480201486de8d66e984a1c483afe8be","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72f7c49faa0828114c2918f5996029efde6dbd5","tid":1762702,"uid":58561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:19:06.000Z","msg":"可唔可以順便寄埋俾施生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"屍永青第二輪整，一定祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n認真既LOCAL其他都有人要寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，E.g. 何韻詩、GPHONE及其他有出席美國聽證會的人、去過美國遊說的人，仲有天琦。不過本地郵件無咁趕，海外郵件趕D。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb46dc64a219ecc939d8bc8e11e51f5e483bdd","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62a384395bd239a0a953b07ddec7783f37cc9945","tid":1762702,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:27:50.000Z","msg":"想寄比冇得返香港嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:51:04.000Z","msg":"有無人代收? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如提供地址幫台灣手足代收? 之前RTHK有個台灣訪問，有個台灣團體幫手安排住屋同工作的? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7641f148579b48edf390837981c7365521d892ac","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23d805b6a71392480526fbfd1b3e60e5aa93d0d7","tid":1762702,"uid":331133,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee9c3f3e2822fb490960a7c937fe43f742fe4e65","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和你寄聖誕咭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n按照你生日月份，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一人寄九張咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>比美國議員Co-sponsors、Trump及Sharon姨姨，感謝佢地推動香港人權與民主法。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收實體聖誕咭會好開心。收到成堆咭，可吸引外媒報導。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，都係另類文宣。我地唔淨係得負面新聞，比D大愛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收咭名單如下，要盡快在12月頭寄出</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=66032ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k421Ov1FTn-ZgCr4b9byaBuXJAgEeAqb/view?usp=sharing</a> (EXCEL)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=3dab49e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rFhqYfgbAbw0_BiqkPzkeReXlwUc_D3u/view?usp=sharing</a>(PDF)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[b]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">綜合各方意見的重點收咭人士(有時間就每個都寄)</span></span></span></strong>:</ins></strong><br />\nMarco Rubio  (Sen.)<br />\nNancy Pelosi (Speaker)<br />\nChristopher H. Smith (Rep.)<br />\nRick Scott  (Sen.)<br />\nJosh Hawley (Sen.)<br />\nTed Cruz (Sen.)<br />\nJames E. Risch (Sen.)<br />\nMitch McConnell (Sen.)<br />\nJames P. McGovern (Rep.)<br />\nAngus S. King Jr. (Sen.)<br />\nDonald Trump (President)<br />\nSharon Hom (Adjunct Professor, New York University)<br />\nSolomon Yue (Committeeman)<br />\n<br />\n有錯漏請更正。<br />\n<br />\n重要事項: 香港郵局已於2019年11月26日截空郵，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但仍可寄出聖誕咭</span></strong>，美國需要7至16個工作天處理，聖誕咭可能遲於聖誕節收到。因此請同時祝福Happy New Year。另外<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家提及Hong Kong Be Water Act</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n郵費: HK$4.9一張咭，重量限制為 20g, 尺吋不大於16.5cm x 24.5cm; 厚度限制為5mm;  如擔心重量超過20g但少於30g，請貼上HK$7.4的郵票。<br />\n<br />\n抱歉暫時未能安排代收郵件。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好幫襯&quot;三中商&quot;之類的書局。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"有創意 我鐘意，<br />\n但唔明，<br />\n「按照你生日月份」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係我8月先寄聖誕咭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"即係如果你一月生日，你就SEND比以下九位議員:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\nBenjamin L. Cardin<br />\nRobert Menendez<br />\nEdward J. Markey<br />\nTom Cotton<br />\nDan Sullivan<br />\nLindsey Graham<br />\nScott Perry<br />\nThomas R. Suozzi<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46c35bd2fba7b9220162ce5c8fca19f04e70c10","tid":1762702,"uid":263648,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"00fef2a02b99411181b5a567fd0ce828ddc9d643","tid":1762702,"uid":96169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:37:44.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n有無搞錯 樓主咁有誠意都無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放心 我會寄"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:57:23.000Z","ms